data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home situated in the heart of the city, with quick access to major routes, Legacy West, Grandscape, and a multitude of activities, shops, dining options to enjoy! The open concept dining and living area offers a warm and inviting ambiance, with features that include vaulted ceilings, a rustic floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace, a wet bar for entertaining guests, and new laminate flooring that flow throughout the main areas. The kitchen is equipped with a new dishwasher and refrigerator that even makes craft ice, making meal preparation a breeze. Additionally, there's a cozy breakfast area for those quick and casual meals. The primary bedroom is complete with a walk-in closet, an updated walk-in shower, and granite countertops. Enjoy the private fully fenced backyard that offers a treehouse size shade tree, perfect spot for relaxation & leisure. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your home sweet home!
